## StudentCard Component

Created a reusable component to display student information.

```tsx
type SCardProps = {
    name: string;
    age: number;
    role: string;
}

function StudentCard(props: SCardProps) {
    return (
        <>
            <h2>{props.name}</h2>
            <p>Age: {props.age}</p>
            <p>Role: {props.role}</p>
        </>
    );
}
```

The component accepts multiple props and renders the student's name, age, and role dynamically.

---

## Component Tree

Built the application using multiple reusable components.

```text
App
│
├── Greetings
├── Header
├── StudentCard
└── Footer
```

React starts with the `App` component and executes each child component to build the complete user interface.

